"{\"uid\": \"travelweekly.com.au-aussie-developer-has-it-in-the-bag-with-olympic-luggage-featuring-a-power-bank\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"RMIT alum Athan Didaskalou will take his Melbourne-based brand July to the world stage this month, as the official luggage supplier to the Australian Olympic Team.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 139, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999990045599086, \"rank\": 9.95440979403687e-07, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When July luggage founder Athan Didaskalou studied at RMIT, he did not want to pay for textbooks.\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So he decided to cover the cost by placing advertisements on the backside of each page.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the concept did not take off, it did not dampen Athan's entrepreneurial spirit.\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"RMIT is very supportive of entrepreneurial ideas.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And for me, that meant a lot,\\\" Didaskalou said.\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since then, there is been maybe 100 ideas.\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some have worked, some have not.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And at the end of the day, July is the one that I have been practising most for.\\\"\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athan studied an Advanced Diploma in Business before completing a Bachelor of Business in Marketing at RMIT.\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Getting to work with people who'd been in the industry, who understood the industry and the commercial realities, not just university projects.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were real,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's definitely one thing I felt that was different about RMIT.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a reality check that helped us grow.\\\"\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athan and his business partner Richard Li founded July in 2019.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Li\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Richard Li\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Li\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Li\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[We] got together talking about what we could do for the industry \\u2026 how much opportunity there was for disruption, to be able to take down the largest global incumbent,\\\"Didaskalousaid.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So how did they do it?\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A direct-to-consumer model with a lower price point - and some innovative features such as built-in ejectable phone charger.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have things like a power bank underneath the handle.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, my business partner and I are now registered inventors, that was a cool thing to add to the list.\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Small ideas, but small ideas combined together into one package makes for a very attractive product.\\\"\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Didaskalousaid his RMIT qualification in marketing has been \\\"one of the strongest\\\" foundations for his business success.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You understand the consumer better, understand how to sell a product, understand how to position it.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And there is no better training than that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"July was recently named the official luggage supplier to the Australian Olympic Team, whose hundreds of athletes will receive a specially designed suitcase when they arrive in Paris.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2090, \"end\": 2113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999990045599086, \"rank\": 9.95440979403687e-07, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2205, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9995546759736239, \"rank\": 0.00044552242812806214, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like the brand itself, the bespoke product is also steeped in Melbourne - taking inspiration from the 1956 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999997507082155, \"rank\": 2.492100229304069e-07, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[The athletes] travel a lot and they need suitcases.\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And we offered a very beautiful design to them and said we'd love to be the official supplier for the team.\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dean of Economics, Finance and Marketing, Professor Heath McDonald said the RMIT College of Business and Law helps students connect with industry professionals.\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It allows them to build their networks and real-life skills and enter the workforce ready to tackle existing business challenges,\\\" Professor McDonald said.\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Athan is a great example of an RMIT alum whose success in solving for customer and business needs is an inspiration to current students who are carving out their own careers.\\\"\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Didaskalourecently returned to RMIT to help grade architecture students, as part of an industry assessment to design a new July shopfront.\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's amazing.\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not believe the energy that young people have.\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To see the energy, to see the ideas, they are so creative.\\\"\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign in to your account  Remember me\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": []}]}"